OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMarmite-owner Unilever bids
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor GSK's consumer arm     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Unilever made an offer of about #50bn  
OL,6, to buy Glaxo Smith Kline's consumer    
OL,7, goods arm in late 2021, it has emerged.
OL,9,FIt means the owner of Marmite, Persil  
OL,10,Fand PG Tips hopes to soon own more     
OL,11,Fhousehold brands including Sensodyne   
OL,12,Ftoothpaste and Panadol.                
OL,14,FIf the sale went ahead, analysts say it
OL,15,Fwould be one of the biggest ever deals 
OL,16,Finvolving London-listed firms.         
OL,18,FThe Sunday Times, which first reported 
OL,19,Fthe move, said GSK rejected the bid for
OL,20,Fbeing too low.                         
